<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="272" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1273,1514]" pageId="11" pageNumber="272">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,1380,1405]" pageId="11" pageNumber="272">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Dorsal-fin rays VII-I, 10; pectoral-fin rays 18–20; total gill rakers 22–23; vertebrae 10 + 15; pyloric caeca 7–9; pored lateral-line scales 48–50; opercular spine absent; maxillary mustache-like processes absent; nublike structures or spine on symphysis of lower jaw absent; ribs on last abdominal vertebra absent; tongue toothless; orbital diameter 12.1–13.6% SL; lower-jaw length 13.4–15.1% SL; body depth 16.4–18.2% SL.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption box="[151,865,1842,1864]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1182185/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="272" startId="11.[151,250,1842,1864]" targetBox="[188,1398,1566,1821]" targetPageId="11">
